title: Haunted Tomb of the Scarlet Lady
story: After being destroyed in a devastating battle a millenium ago the tomb of the Scarlet Lady remained uninhabited. Lately an undead albino eagle has made its lair here.

notes.text: A great wooden double door with a keyhole on the western wall of the small room.
A corpse of a gnome, a scimitar close to it.
A trunk holds a strange, sticky to touch object.
A heart-shaped key in a medium crate.
